Got it.

875
00:36:14,000 --> 00:36:15,070
I tell all my friends.

876
00:36:15,070 --> 00:36:16,150
No matter what it is.

877
00:36:16,150 --> 00:36:17,710
Personal, business, important, trivial,

878
00:36:17,710 --> 00:36:18,790
fun, or just idle chatter,

879
